        <h4 id="trail-guide">Trail Guide</h4>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Duration</strong>: 2.3 miles, Ascent = 1:30, Descent (hurrying) = 1:00</li>
  <li>Best maps:
    <ul>
      <li>‚ÄúBenton Mackaye Trail: Section 6 Shallowford Bridge to Weaver Creek Rd‚Äù (8.5‚Äùx11‚Äù single sheet handout from Menton Mackaye Trail Association)</li>
      <li>National Geographic Trails Illustrated Map #777: Springer &amp; Cohutta Mountains.  ‚ÄúWest Side‚Äù, map grid H9</li>
