  <li><strong>Navigation</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>Marked, obvious trailhead on left as you enter parking area.</li>
      <li>At 0.6 miles, BMT enters from right. You continue straight/left, following BMT as it goes north and then turns west.</li>
      <li>Near the end of your route, you‚Äôll hike around the summit.  It will be to your left.  At 2.2 miles, on the north side of the summit, take an acute left onto a faint trail up the ridge to the summit.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>GPS tracks/waypoints</strong>:
    <ul>
      <li>Trailhead: 34.78085, -84.3118, altitude 2322‚Äô</li>
